Frontiers in Neuroscience 05 frontiersin.org
3. Directed frequency band component exchange: swap specific frequency band components between paired low-variance and high-variance samples. 4. Wavelet packet reconstruction for synthetic sample generation: reconstruct the modified time-frequency components to generate new synthetic EEG samples.
