For each class of EEG signals, 5-level wavelet packet decomposition is performed using the db4 wavelet basis. Subsequently, directed frequency band exchange is implemented. Given that motor imagery EEG information is primarily concentrated in the α rhythm (8–13 Hz) and β rhythm (14–30 Hz) (Wu et al., 2025), sample pairs
